node.text:
Barcelona from night to day via @world_walkerz. ✨ Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on viewfervor.com (link in my bio: @viewfervor)

Barcelona is a cosmopolitan city in the Mediterranean coast of northeastern Spain, capital of the autonomous community of Catalonia and is known for its unique culture, exquisite cuisine, diverse art and spectacular architecture. 🇪🇸

Save this post if you wanna visit and add these to your bucket list! 📝

𝟭𝟬 𝗕𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗧𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴𝘀 𝘁𝗼 𝗗𝗼 𝗶𝗻 𝗕𝗮𝗿𝗰𝗲𝗹𝗼𝗻𝗮
1. Visit La Sagrada Família.
2. Get amazed by Antoni Gaudí at Casa Batlló.
3. Street food tour at La Boqueria. 
4. Enjoy a getaway at Parc del Laberint d'Horta. 
5. Immerse in the Picasso world at the Picasso Museum.
6. Take a walk at the cosmopolitan street of La Rambla. 
7. Discover traditional Catalan folk music at The Palau de la Música Catalana.
8. Beach day at La Barceloneta beach.
9. Shopping time at Portal del Angel or Passeig de Gracia.
10. Hang out at night in El Born.

Who would you visit this awe-inspiring city with?

📸 @world_walkerz
📍 Barcelona, Spain
